          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="right-content">
            <p>Our licensed, factory-trained technicians repair all Haier stove models, including:</p>
            <ul>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Gas Stoves</strong> – Compact and full-size sealed burner models (e.g., QGAS740RMSS, HCR2250AGS)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Electric Stoves</strong> – Smooth-top and coil burner models (e.g., QAS740RMSS)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Dual-Fuel Ranges</strong> – Gas cooktop with electric oven combinations</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Induction Cooktops</strong> – Precise, fast-heating cooking surfaces</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Slide-In & Freestanding Ranges</strong> – For standard and small kitchen layouts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-3">
