              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Igniter not sparking or clicking</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Touch panel or knobs not responding</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Error codes</strong> like F1, F2, or F5</li>
